data.description: ***  PRICE REDUCED ***The Lakes in Menifee! ***  This single-story home features an open floor plan, built in cabinetry, upgraded flooring, designer paint, spacious bedrooms, and is upgraded throughout. *** The oversized kitchen is an entertainer's dream that features granite counters, Stainless Steel Appliances,  ample storage and cabinet space, and last but not least, an island with plenty of room for seating or display your food dead smack in the center of the kitchen at your next event! *** The family room is very bright and cheery with large bright windows, perfect for family gatherings or entertaining.  *** The primary bedroom has a huge walk-in closet as well as a bathroom with a separate shower and soaking tub, dual sinks, and a vanity. ***  A large backyard  *** The Gated Lakes Community offers 3 lakes for fishing, pools with waterslides and splash pad, parks, walking trails, exercise room, clubhouse with outdoor BBQ area and patio area with fireplace.   ***  SOLAR - Equipment Purchase (Sunnovo) NOT Power Purchase.  Fixed payment of $228.09.  NO INCREASES!  This will save you loads of money!  Edison bills available to review!
